title: You Shut Your Whore Mouth
author: VD
content_html:
To quote the great John Bradley, “I’m sure you all know where Booster Patrol weighs in on this Very Important Topic.”

If it doesn’t have a guitar solo, is it really even a song? And what is this “unplugged” concept of which they speak?
